import {Fragment} from 'react';
import Box from "@mui/material/Box";
import AppBar from '@mui/material/AppBar';
import Typography from '@mui/material/Typography';
import Button from '@mui/material/Button';
import HelpIcon from '@mui/icons-material/Help';


function Home(){
    return(
        <Fragment>
            <Box sx={{ flexGrow: 1 }}>
                <AppBar position="static" sx={{backgroundColor: 'rgb(50,53,60)'}} >
                    {/* Possibly change to image of logo instead */}
                    <Box
                        align='left'
                        sx={{width:140}}
                    >
                       <Typography
                        variant="h6"
                        noWrap
                        align='left'
                        
                        >
                            MealsFromDirt
                        </Typography>  
                    </Box>
                    <Box
                        sx={{width:140}}
                    >
                        <Button
                            align='right'
                            width='50'
                        >
                            <HelpIcon fontSize='large' />
                        </Button> 
                    </Box>   
                </AppBar>
                
            </Box>


            <Box>
                Image
            </Box>
            <Box>
                Text Bar Input
            </Box>
            <Box>
                Enter Button
            </Box>
        </Fragment>
    )
}

export default Home;
